# Phase 1.5 Organization Setup Complete

## Summary

Organization setup (districts and stores management) is now complete.

## Features Implemented

1. Districts CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
2. Stores CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
3. Organization Setup page in admin
4. Seed data for demo

## Database Tables

- `districts` - District management
- `stores` - Store management
- `roles` - Role management

## Seed Data

- 4 Districts (Northeast, Southeast, Midwest, West Coast)
- 9 Stores distributed across districts
- 6 Default roles

## Next Phase

Phase 2: User Invitation System
